** APC UPS HIGH LOAD WARNING **

Device:    ${NodeName}
IP:        ${IP_Address}
Location:  ${Location}
Time:      ${DateTime}

WARNING: This UPS is operating at or above 80% output load capacity.

High load reduces available runtime during a power outage and
increases stress on the UPS and battery.

Recommended actions:
  1. Review connected equipment at this location
  2. Consider load balancing across additional UPS units
  3. Evaluate if additional capacity is needed at: ${Location}
  4. Check for any newly added equipment drawing unexpected load

Alert threshold:  80% load
Reset threshold:  70% load

APC Device Web UI: http://${IP_Address}

-- SolarWinds Automated Alert

** APC UPS HIGH LOAD ALERT CLEARED **

Device:    ${NodeName}
IP:        ${IP_Address}
Location:  ${Location}
Time:      ${DateTime}

UPS output load has dropped below 70% and returned to normal levels.
No further action required unless load reduction was unplanned.

APC Device Web UI: http://${IP_Address}

-- SolarWinds Automated Alert
